## 7. KEY API CLASSES & METHODS

### SpatialDb
- `init()` - Initialize database
- `loadOsmFromOverpassApi(params)` - Load OSM data
- `loadCustomLayer(params)` - Load GeoJSON
- `loadCsv(params)` - Load CSV
- `loadJson(params)` - Load JSON
- `loadGridLayer(params)` - Create grid
- `spatialJoin(params)` - Spatial join operation
- `buildHeatmap(params)` - Create heatmap grid
- `rawQuery(params)` - Raw SQL
- `getLayer(name)` - Export as GeoJSON
- `getTableData(params)` - Export as objects
- `getLayerTables()` - List geometry tables
- `getOsmBoundingBox()` - OSM extent
- `getBoundingBoxFromLayer(name)` - Layer extent
- `updateTable(params)` - Update/replace table
- `removeLayer(name)` - Delete table
- `setWorkspace(name)` - Switch workspace
- `getWorkspaces()` - List workspaces
- `getCurrentWorkspace()` - Active workspace

### AutkMap
- `init()` - Initialize WebGPU
- `loadGeoJsonLayer(name, geojson, type?)` - Add layer
- `loadGeoTiffLayer(name, data, type)` - Add raster
- `updateRenderInfoProperty(layer, property, value)` - Style layer
- `updateGeoJsonLayerThematic(layer, geojson, fn, groupById?)` - Apply thematic coloring
- `updateLayerGeometry(layer, data)` - Update geometry
- `draw()` - Start render loop
- `camera` - Camera accessor
- `boundingBox` - Bounding box getter/setter
- `mapEvents` - Event emitter (MapEvent.PICK)

### GeojsonCompute
- `computeFunctionIntoProperties(params)` - Execute WGSL on features

### Chart Classes (Barchart, Scatterplot, ParallelCoordinates)
- `setHighlightedIds(ids)` - Highlight rows
- `plotEvents.on(event, handler)` - Listen for interactions

